    "en": {
      "name": "Azamina Ofeiletis",
      "effect": "During the Main Phase: Reveal 1 \"Azamina\" Fusion Monster in your Extra Deck and send 1 \"Sinful Spoils\" card from your hand and/or field to the GY for every 4 Levels the revealed monster has (if those cards are Set, reveal them), then Special Summon it. (This is treated as a Fusion Summon.) During your Main Phase: You can banish this card from your GY, then target 1 \"Azamina\" monster in your GY; Special Summon it. You can only use 1 \"Azamina Ofeiletis\" effect per turn, and only once that turn.",
      "official": false
    },
